# Implementation Plan - SuperThanks Feature (Expanded)

This plan covers the full implementation of the "SuperThanks" feature, enabling users to send gratitude messages to other users, and receivers to see a confetti celebration.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> Database indexes might be required for efficient queries on `super_thanks`.
> This feature relies on the user being logged in via Google.

